@startuml Booking_Saga_Compensation
title Booking Saga - Сценарии компенсации

participant "Booking (Orchestrator)" as booking #LightBlue
participant "Fraud" as fraud
participant "Pricing" as pricing
participant "Driver" as driver
participant "Notification" as notification

== Сценарий A: Фрод обнаружен (шаг 2) ==

booking -> fraud: CheckBookingFraudCmd
fraud --> booking: FraudDetected (risk_score: 0.85)

booking -> booking: CancelBookingCmd (статус: CANCELLED_FRAUD)
booking ->> notification: NotifyPassengerCmd ("Заказ отменен")

== Сценарий B: Нет водителей (шаг 5, таймаут) ==

booking -> driver: FindDriverCmd
driver --> booking: DriverNotFound (timeout 30s)

booking -> driver: RetryFindDriverCmd (расширение радиуса +2 км)
driver --> booking: DriverNotFound

booking -> driver: RetryFindDriverCmd (расширение радиуса +4 км)
driver --> booking: DriverNotFound

note over booking: Все 3 попытки исчерпаны
booking -> booking: CancelBookingCmd (статус: CANCELLED_NO_DRIVER)
booking ->> notification: NotifyPassengerCmd ("Нет доступных водителей")

== Сценарий C: Водитель отменил после назначения ==

booking -> driver: FindDriverCmd
driver --> booking: DriverAssigned (driver_42)

... 10 сек позже ...

driver --> booking: DriverCancelled (driver_42)

booking -> driver: ReleaseDriverCmd (driver_42) (штраф к рейтингу)
booking -> driver: RetryFindDriverCmd (новый поиск, исключая driver_42)
booking ->> notification: NotifyPassengerCmd ("Ищем другого водителя")
driver --> booking: DriverAssigned (driver_87)
booking -> booking: BookingConfirmed

@enduml
